data.description: Seller offering $10,000 Buyer Credit! Welcome to this spacious and inviting 3 bedroom, 2 bath home nestled in the heart of beautiful Chowchilla. Offering over 2,000 sf of living space, the open floor plan creates an airy and welcoming atmosphere, making it perfect for entertaining friends and family. The living room is open to the dining space and kitchen.  The three bedrooms are roomy and comfortable, providing plenty of space for relaxation and privacy.  You'll love the master bedroom and ensuite offering a sunken, jetted tub!  Step outside to find a an inground pool, ideal for enjoying those hot Chowchilla summers.  The lot is generously sized allowing for additional patio space.  Whether you’re lounging poolside or hosting a barbecue, this space is designed for making lasting memories. This home is conveniently located in the heart of Chowchilla, close to schools, parks, and all the amenities the area has to offer. Don’t miss this opportunity to make this beautiful property your own.
